headline.main: Missions Return to London; U.S. HEWS TO PLAN TO HELP RUSSIANS

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Oct. 9 (AP) -- The British and American supply missions returned to England from Moscow today for a supreme effort to sustain imperiled Russia to the last, on the theory that if Moscow falls the armies beyond the Urals still
